      "content": "i hear u, but it feels like you're saying free trade is the only \"real\" way to run an economy and everything else is just a mistake. if a country is losing all its manufacturing jobs and its middle class is dying, isn't using tariffs actually the most logical and correct response to that? isn't that just common sense?",
